<para id="element-60">
Here, speed at maximum compression is zero. Thus, 
<m:math>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> K </m:mi>
<m:mi> f </m:mi>
</m:msub>
</m:math>
 is zero.
</para>

<para id="element-61">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
